{
  "stem": "11089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was there only-- not even two years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because he was more Zionistic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Avraham.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Avraham Katz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother's name was Katz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was his real--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her real brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Avraham Katz And he very ear-- very long [INAUDIBLE] earlier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was like a soldier and-- with the yellow band, you know, in Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but not-- not trusted with a rifle or with ammunition.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had their-- they were only like workers to help out digging ditches, and supplying food, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to wear a yellow band with a special cap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to go myself, but I was too young.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wouldn't accept me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to-- you had to be 19 or over, or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And secondly, I hesitated even because my father wasn't with us when we were taken to the-- to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- and I said to myself, I am the oldest in the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe I should go with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe, you know, from time to time she needs me to help her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I wanted-- one time, my mother told me to go into this-- it was called Hungarian munkaszolgálat, working battalion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I was too young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't accept me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was there, my uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] See, next-- next to the torturing of the death camps, like Auschwitz, Birkenau, Majdanck, and so on, so on, the next step of torturing, and also leading to death, were those Hungarian munkaszolgálat, battalions of working.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Very few survived from there either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They-- they-- they died from hunger, or from dirt, or from freezing, who knows what.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
